OL,3,C'We would have had a lot more years':
OL,4,CFather-of-five death sparks fury
OL,6,FA family in Alderney are calling for
OL,7,Fan independent investigation into the
OL,8,Fdeath of a father-of-five after he
OL,9,Fdied following a misdiagnosis and
OL,10,Fdelayed medical evacuations.
OL,12,FJohn Charles Frederick Yeates visited
OL,13,Fthe Mignot Memorial Hospital (MMH) in
OL,14,FAlderney multiple times in January and
OL,15,FFebruary 2026, complaining about his
OL,16,Fsevere upper back and shoulder pain.
OL,18,FJohn was evacuated to Guernsey twice
OL,19,Fduring that period after doctors
OL,20,Frealised he had had a heart attack.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
