CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1780679163
OL,3,C'We would have had a lot more years':
OL,4,CFather-of-five death sparks fury
OL,6,FHowever, both times John's medical
OL,7,Fevacuation transport was delayed both
OL,8,Ftimes.
OL,10,FHis family says the second proved to
OL,11,Fbe too late. John's wife, Tina, and
OL,12,Fhis brother allege that a heart attack
OL,13,Fwas misdiagnosed as muscle strain.
OL,15,FThey told ITV News that John's death
OL,16,Fhappened too soon and was avoidable.
OL,18,F"I'm angry that someone could be
OL,19,Ftreated the way he was," Tina said.
OL,20,F"Especially him being misdiagnosed in
OL,21,Fthe first place."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1780679163
OL,3,C'We would have had a lot more years':
OL,4,CFather-of-five death sparks fury
OL,6,FThe family also claim that delays
OL,7,Fproved fatal when John suffered a
OL,8,Fheart attack and sepsis.
OL,10,FJohn's family has shared with ITV News
OL,11,Fresponses from the Health and Social
OL,12,FCare (HSC) department to the family's
OL,13,Fcomplaint, arguing that the assessment
OL,14,Fwas appropriate at the time.
OL,16,FThey said that they found no evidence
OL,17,Fthat the initial diagnosis was
OL,18,Finadequate or that there were delays
OL,19,Fthat contributed to John's death.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
