OL,3,C'We would have had a lot more years':
OL,4,CFather-of-five death sparks fury
OL,6,FOne response reads: "I appreciate the
OL,7,Fdelay to your father's transfer must
OL,8,Fhave been very worrying for you all,
OL,9,Fbut poor weather that day meant that
OL,10,Fit was not safe for Aurigny aircraft
OL,11,Fto fly."
OL,13,F"It was unsafe for your father to be
OL,14,Ftransferred by boat; the only other
OL,15,Foption at that time was a helicopter."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
