CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1780679163
OL,3,C'We would have had a lot more years':
OL,4,CFather-of-five death sparks fury
OL,6,FRegarding the second delay, they
OL,7,Fwrote: "As your father was already
OL,8,Freceiving all the treatment he would
OL,9,Fhave had at (Princess Elizabeth
OL,10,FHospital), there was no immediate need
OL,11,Ffor life-saving treatment - the
OL,12,Fcriteria for transfer by lifeboat or
OL,13,Fhelicopter were not met."
OL,15,FHealth bosses told ITV News that
OL,16,Fthey'd be responding directly to the
OL,17,Ffamily about their continued concern.
OL,26,@qD@MpmrD@Ipn
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/8
