PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1780679163
OL,3,C'We would have had a lot more years':
OL,4,CFather-of-five death sparks fury
OL,6,FJohn's family contest the facts of
OL,7,Fthose responses, arguing that the
OL,8,FHSC's conclusions relied on
OL,9,F"inconsistencies" and "omissions of
OL,10,Fcritical clinical facts" such as the
OL,11,Fpatient's sepsis and diabetic status.
OL,13,FThey also say that it is "not
OL,14,Fcredible" to claim John was receiving
OL,15,F"all necessary care" in Alderney,
OL,16,Fciting the lack of "specialist
OL,17,Fcardiology" facilities.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/8
