PN,38407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1780679163
OL,3,C'We would have had a lot more years':
OL,4,CFather-of-five death sparks fury
OL,6,FMedical evacuations have proved a
OL,7,Fsignificant problem in Alderney in
OL,8,Frecent times. There were 17
OL,9,Fevacuations last month, according to a
OL,10,Ftown hall meeting held on the island
OL,11,Flast week - a figure that is
OL,12,Fsignificantly above average.
OL,14,FThe issue has also been discussed as
OL,15,Fpart of plans to revamp the island's
OL,16,Frunway, currently scheduled to take
OL,17,Fplace over the course of five months
OL,18,Fin 2027.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
